# Privacy Policy — Luna Window

Effective date: 2026-01-11

Luna Window (“the App”) is designed to work offline.

## Data We Collect

- We do not collect personal data.
- We do not use analytics or third‑party tracking SDKs in the MVP.

## Data Stored on Your Device

- Preferences (selected scene, sound, timer, toggles) are stored locally on your device.
- If you import audio files, the App stores a local copy in the app sandbox so the App can play it. You can delete imported audio in Settings.

## Purchases

- In‑app purchases are processed by Apple. We do not receive your payment information.

## Contact

- Support: qq260316514@gmail.com

